Description: Shoulder sherd of Attic black-glazed pottery dinos with turn to rim; glazed black on interior (streaky) and exterior.
Curator's comments: Almost certainly from the same dinos as 1886,0401.677-80 and 1965,0930.511, dedicated by Phanes, though the glaze is substantially less streaky on the interior.
Bibliographic references: Villing et al 2013-2015 / Naukratis: Greeks in Egypt (GA.0989)
